Privacy Policy
Effective Date: October 23, 2018
This Privacy Policy applies to mahjongllc.com web site and all mobile games published by Mahjong, OOO.
We reserve the right to change our practices and this Privacy Policy at any time. 
We encourage you to check this page regularly so that you know our current practices.
What Data We Collect
We do not collect any personal information except e-mail addresses when you contact us in order to reply to you. 
In this case some non-personal information is also collected (web browser user agent info and supported language) 
in order to improve support service.
Some non-personal technical information is collected automatically when you visit our web site as a part of
common web server usage practices. This information includes IP address, web browser user agent and time of the visit.
Why Do We Collect Your Data
We use the information we collect for providing and improving the quality of our games and technical support.
Who Can See Your Data
We do not share, public or sell collected data.
In order to combat fraud and illegal activity, we may provide data to public authorities in response to lawful requests.
Cookies and Similar Technologies
We do not use cookies and any user tracking technologies.
We do not use Advertising Identifiers.
Third party services
We do not use any third party tools, libraries and services, which can collect any personal or non-personal information except
standard web server log files analyzing tools.
Age Limits
We do not intentionally gather personal data from users who are under the age of 13. 
In the event that we learn that we have collected personal information from a child under age 13, 
we will delete that information as quickly as possible.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy please
contact us
